{"TopicId":207785,"ForumId":24,"TopicTitle":"Captcha","CreatedByName":"redglyph","CreatedById":221035,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-16T14:55:09Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"redglyph","CreatedById":221035,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-16T14:55:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello, I\u0027ve just registered but I almost gave up on your registration captcha, it\u0027s unreadable and doesn\u0027t work well, had to re-do it 4 times.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWay to welcome people :p\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-16T15:05:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the Forums \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/221035-redglyph/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022221035\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/221035-redglyph/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@redglyph\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027re sorry you encountered some issues, but this is the first we\u0027ve heard of it.\u00A0\u00A0 We\u0027ll take a look.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jcklemme","CreatedById":62597,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-16T19:06:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224117901\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207785\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221650121519\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the Forums \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/221035-redglyph/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022221035\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/221035-redglyph/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@redglyph\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027re sorry you encountered some issues, but this is the first we\u0027ve heard of it.\u00A0\u00A0 We\u0027ll take a look.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s exceptionally difficult on mobile due to the screen size and the UI not reacting well to touch controls.\u00A0 On desktop it works as intended.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-16T19:08:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224118062\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207785\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221650135961\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262597\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jcklemme\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Jcklemme said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s exceptionally difficult on mobile due to the screen size and the UI not reacting well to touch controls.\u00A0 On desktop it works as intended.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAhh yes.. the beautiful Invision mobile interface.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 Yeah, we pass on to Invision quite a number of mobile bugs regularly.\u00A0\u00A0 The good news is.... you don\u0027t need to do the captcha again!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jcklemme","CreatedById":62597,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-16T19:11:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224118064\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207785\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221650136130\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAhh yes.. the beautiful Invision mobile interface.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 Yeah, we pass on to Invision quite a number of mobile bugs regularly.\u00A0\u00A0 The good news is.... you don\u0027t need to do the captcha again!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProper forums aren\u0027t meant to be used on a mobile device anyhow, mobile devices encourage low effort posts due to their interface.\u00A0 Phones are more suited to posting on Twitter or other places with a character limit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}